00:34:17.125 --> 00:34:20.360
Sanjao sam da sam te dozivao
a ti se nisi odazvala.

00:34:21.963 --> 00:34:24.799
Nastavio sam da te zovem,
ali te nisam našao.

00:34:27.869 --> 00:34:30.872
